<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She has a keen eye for style and co-owns a fashion boutique with her sister.</p>

<p>And Francesca Allen was looking typically chic in an all black ensemble, as she left her offices in Loughton, Essex, on Wednesday afternoon.</p>

<p>The former Love Island contestant, 24, wore a longline top teamed with a pair of flared trousers and a scarf, which she layered with a leather jacket. </p>

<p>Chic: Francesca Allen was looking typically chic in an all black ensemble, as she left her offices in Loughton, Essex, on Wednesday afternoon</p>

<p>Francesca added a touch of glitz to her look with a pair metallic silver trainers, while showcasing her penchant for designer goods with a simple black Prada bag.</p>

<p>The reality star wore her brunette locks in a bouncy blown out style, while enhancing her striking looks with a full coat of make-up in neutral shades.</p>

<p>She was seen chatting away on her mobile phone as she left the premises. </p>

<p>Francesca's boutique is a joint venture with her sister Claudia Allen, who also designs jewellery for her business French Fashion House.</p>

<p>All black everything: The former Love Island contestant, 24, wore a longline top teamed with a pair of flared trousers and a scarf, which she layered with a leather jacket</p>

<p>Details: Francesca added a touch of glitz to her look with a pair metallic silver trainers, while showcasing her penchant for designer goods with a simple black Prada bag</p>

<p>Over the summer months Francesca enjoyed several holidays and her Instagram was littered with sizzling bikini snaps.</p>

<p>Aside from her frequent getaways, Francesca was spotted cosying up to a new man during a boozy night out in London earlier this summer.</p>

<p>She looked to be on cloud nine as she got up close and personal with Edward Crossan, vice chairman of London-based waste management company Powerday.</p>

<p>The TV personality, who is family friends with Edward, put on a very affectionate display with the hunk who was previously been linked to TOWIE's Amber Turner.</p>

<p>Who's that? She was seen chatting away on her mobile phone as she left the premises</p>

<p>In May last year, Edward was seen enjoying a jaunt on a yacht in Ibiza with TOWIE star Amber, 27, who is currently dating Dan Edgar.</p>

<p>The accomplished businessman was named vice chairman of his father's company in January and is featured on the company's website.</p>

<p>His working title is described on the website as: 'Edward joined the family business in 2007, starting as a machine driver and has worked in various roles within the company to now being a director overseeing the development of the business.'</p>

<p>MailOnline contacted Francesca's representatives for further comment at the time of publication.</p>

